  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to printproto</title>

    <para>
      The <application>printproto</application> package provides the protocol
      headers for the <xref linkend="libxp"/> package.
    </para>

    
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&printproto-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

  <bridgehead renderas="sect3">printproto Dependencies</bridgehead>

  <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Required</bridgehead>
  <para role="required">
    <ulink url="&blfs-svn;/x/xorg7.html#xorg-env">Xorg build environment</ulink>
    (should be set for the following instructions to work)
  </para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of printproto</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>printproto</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure $XORG_CONFIG</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the &root; user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

